\"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giannis Antetokounmpo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\"}, {\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995454014668983, \"rank\": 0.00045479838058021683, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A floater from Shai Gilgeous-Alexander with 42 seconds left essentially iced the game before a pair of free throws from Jamal Murray put the final touches on Canada\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s first win in Olympic basketball in nearly a quarter-century.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shai_Gilgeous-Alexander\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shai Gilgeous-Alexander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shai_Gilgeous-Alexander\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shai_Gilgeous-Alexander\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamal Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former Gonzaga standouts Andrew Nembhard and Kelly Olynyk both contributed off the bench in the victory.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.185795076264397