ng.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saint Mary\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s standout Jock Landale was a problem for the Spaniards on the inside, as the 6-foot-11 Melbourne native had 20 points, nine rebounds and five assists.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jock_Landale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jock Landale\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jock_Landale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jock_Landale\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.5760469847448284, \"rank\": 0.5993334202123708, \"text\": \"Spaniards\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Combined with an all-around exhibition from Josh Giddey (17 points, eight rebounds and eight assists) and shotmaking from Patty Mills (19 points and three 3-pointers) Australia overwhelmed in a 92-80 victory that saw Spain shoot less than 50% in the paint.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9999997712657467, \"rank\": 2.281949250436001e-07, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giddey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Giddey\"}, {\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_Mills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Patty Mills\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_Mills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_Mills\"}, {\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5244566100193998, \"rank\": 0.6032823171341698, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999837477845, \"rank\": 1.5679515374242605e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada has an advantage with its slew of talented NBA-level guards, but the Aussies arguably have a slight edge with its size up front.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9836105762297721, \"rank\": 0.01622593362615182, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadians allowed the Greeks to shoot 14-of-24 (58%) on attempts in the painted area, granted most of those opportunities were created by Antetokounmpo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s uncanny ability at getting to the rim.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aussies have no such luxury in their frontcourt, though if there are any weaknesses with thi